en (2014 film)|Queen]]'' || [[Indian Film Festival of Melbourne]] || Best Actress || {{won}} || align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite news|title=Big B honoured with International Screen Icon award at IFFM |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news-interviews/Big-B-honoured-with-International-Screen-Icon-award-at-IFFM/articleshow/34626659.cms |accessdate=15 July 2014 |newspaper=The Times of India |date=4 May 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507044218/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news-interviews/Big-B-honoured-with-International-Screen-Icon-award-at-IFFM/articleshow/34626659.cms |archivedate= 7 May 2014 }}</ref>\n|-\n| Jagran Film Festival || Best Actor (Female) || {{won}} || align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite news|title=5th Jagran Film Festival concludes with award ceremony |url=http://www.mid-day.com/articles/5th-jagran-film-festival-concludes-with-award-ceremony/15642169#sthash.s2Rho6K2.dpuf |work=[[Mid Day]] |date=29 September 2014 |accessdate=18 April 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418072302/http://www.mid-day.com/articles/5th-jagran-film-festival-concludes-with-award-ceremony/15642169 |archivedate=18 April 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Stardust Awards]] || [[Stardust Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] || {{won}} || align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Winners of Stardust Awards 2014 |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/7635 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |date=15 December 2014 |accessdate=15 December 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215100048/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/7635 |archivedate=15 December 2014 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Stardust Award for Star of the Year \u2013 Female|Star of the Year \u2013 Female]] || {{nom}} || align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite web|title=Nominations for Stardust Awards 2014 |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/mov