11) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/537945 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=29 March 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231174646/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/537945 |archivedate=31 December 2013 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Miley Naa Miley Hum]]''\n| 2011\n| {{Sort|Shrivastava|Anishka Shrivastava}}\n|{{Sort|Khan|Tanveer Khan}}\n|\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Miley Naa Miley Hum (2011) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/536572 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=29 March 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727140718/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/536572 |archivedate=27 July 2014 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Tezz]]''\n| 2012\n| Nikita Malhotra\n|[[Priyadarshan]]\n|\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Tezz (2012) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/537946 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=29 March 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226030924/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/537946 |archivedate=26 February 2014 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Shootout at Wadala]]''\n| 2013\n| {{Sort|Joshi|Vidya Joshi}}\n|{{Sort|Gupta|[[Sanjay Gupta (director)|Sanjay Gupta]]}}\n|\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Shootout at Wadala (2012) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/547370 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=29 March 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130624024324/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/547370 |archivedate=24 June 2013 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Krrish 3]]''\n| 2013\n| Kaya\n|{{Sort|Roshan|[[Rakesh Roshan]]}}\n|\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Krrish 3 (2013) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/525408 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=29 March 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=