i|Aanand L. Rai}}\n|National Film Award for Best Actress<br>[[Filmfare Critics Award for Best Actress]]<br>Nominated\u2014Filmfare Award for Best Actress\n| align=\"center\"|<ref name=\"tanu2\">{{cite web|title=Check out: Kangna Ranaut's warming up session on Tanu Weds Manu sets |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/7558 |accessdate=27 November 2014 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |date=25 November 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141126021756/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/movies/features/type/view/id/7558 |archivedate=26 November 2014 }}</ref><br/><ref>{{cite web|title=Tanu Weds Manu Returns (2015) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/547997 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=14 January 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330083932/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/547997 |archivedate=30 March 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[I Love NY (2015 film)|I Love NY]]''\n| 2015\n| {{Sort|Verma|Tikku Verma}}\n|{{Sort|Rao|Radhika Rao}}<br/>Vinay Sapru\n|\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|last=Vats |first=Rohit |title=I Love NY review: Kangana Ranaut doesn\u2019t disappoint, again |url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/movie-reviews/i-love-ny-review-kangana-ranaut-doesn-t-disappoint-again/article1-1367816.aspx |accessdate=11 July 2015 |work=Hindustan Times |date=10 July 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711093423/http://www.hindustantimes.com/movie-reviews/i-love-ny-review-kangana-ranaut-doesn-t-disappoint-again/article1-1367816.aspx |archivedate=11 July 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Katti Batti]]''\n| 2015\n| Payal\n|{{Sort|Advani|[[Nikhil Advani]]}}\n| \n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Katti Batti (2015) |url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/746613 |publisher=Bollywood Hungama |accessdate=14 January 2015 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113063107/http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/moviemicro/cast/id/746613 |archivedate=13 January 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Rangoon (2017 Hindi film)|Rangoon]]''\n| 2017\n| Julia\n| {{Sort|Bhardwaj|[[Vishal Bhardwaj]]}}\n| Nominated\u2014Filmfare Critics Award for Best Actress\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Rangoon is a grand hotchpotch! |url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/review-rangoon-is-a-grand-hotchpotch/20170224.htm |last=Verma |first=Sukanya |publisher=Rediff.com |date=24 February 2017 |accessdate=25 February 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225024840/http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/review-rangoon-is-a-grand-hotchpotch/20170224.htm |archivedate=25 February 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Simran (film)|Simran]]''\n| 2017\n| Praful Patel\n| {{Sort|Mehta|[[Hansal Mehta]]}}\n| Also co-Writer\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|last=Coutinhol |first=Natasha |title=Kangana Ranaut turns scriptwriter |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/kangana-ranautturns-scriptwriter/articleshow/58374819.cms |accessdate=11 May 2017 |work=The Times of India |date=26 April 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427042648/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/kangana-ranautturns-scriptwriter/articleshow/58374819.cms |archivedate=27 April 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Manikarnika: The Queen of Jhansi]]''\n| 2019\n| [[Rani Laxmibai]]\n| {{Sort|Krish|[[Krish (director)|Radha Krishna Jagarlamudi]]}}<br/>Herself\n| Nominated\u2014Filmfare Award for Best Actress\n| align=\"center\"|<ref>{{cite news|last=Lohana|first=Avinash|title=Krish on directing Kangana Ranaut-starrer Manikarnika{{mdash}}The Queen of Jhansi|url=http://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/krish-on-directing-kangana-ranaut-starrer-manikarnika-the-queen-of-jhansi/articleshow/58617059.cms|accessdate=11 May 2017|work=Mumbai Mirror|date=11 M