e}}\n|}\n\n==Tours==\n'''Supporting'''\n*[[Clairo]] \u2013 [[Immunity Tour]] (2019)\n*[[The 1975]] \u2013 [[Music for Cars Tour]] (2020)\n*The 1975 \u2013 [[Notes on a Conditional Form Tour]] (2020)\n\n== Awards and nominations ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Year\n!Organization\n!Award\n!Work\n!Result\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" |2019\n|[[NME]]\n|The NME 100\n|Herself\n|{{Included}}\n|<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-\n|[[2019 UK Music Video Awards|UK Music Video Awards]]\n|[[2019 UK Music Video Awards#Video Genre Categories|Best Rock Video - Newcomer]]\n|\"Disappear\"\n|{{Nominated}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ukmva.com/130-nominations-2019|title=video genre categories - ukmva 2019|website=[[UK Music Video Awards]]|url-status=live|access-date=November 27, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Amazon Music]]\n|Ones to Watch 2020\n| rowspan=\"6\" |Herself\n|{{Included}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.musicweek.com/digital/read/amazon-music-reveals-ones-to-watch-2020-line-up/078192|title=Amazon Music reveals Ones To Watch 2020 line-up|last=Paine|first=Andre|date=25 November 2019|website=[[Music Week]]|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=4 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[DIY (magazine)|DIY]]\n|Class of 2020\n|{{Included}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://diymag.com/2019/12/03/diy-class-of-2020-dry-cleaning-squid-beabadoobee-december-january-issue|title=DIY\u2019S Class of 2020 - Featuring Dry Cleaning, Squid, Beabadoobee & MORE - Issue is Out Now!|last=|first=|date=December 6, 2019|website=[[DIY (magazine)|DIY]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=December 15, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Dork (magazine)|Dork]]\n|Hype List 2020\n|{{Included}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.readdork.com/features/hype-list-2020-beabadoobee|title=Hype List 2020: Beabadoobee|last=Konemann|first=Liam|date=November 26, 2019|website=[[Dork (magazine)|Dork]]|language=en|url-status=live|access-date=December 15, 2019}}</ref>\n